<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢٧٥٧ - ش ت ر]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>شتِرَ يَشتَر، شَتَرًا، فهو أشتَرُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• شتِر الشَّيءُ:</span> انقطع وانشقّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• شتِر الشَّخصُ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١ - انقلب جفْنُ عينه <span class="c1">"رجلٌ أشترُ"</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٢ - انشقّت شفتُه السُّفْلَى <span class="c1">"عمليّة تجميليَّة لطفلةٍ شتراءُ"</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>